ippett, licencjonowanego na podstawie CC-BY-SA, pełna lista współpracowników na Wikipedii.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"喬·蒂皮特（Joe Tippett，1982 年 3 月 1 日-），美國演員。","name":"喬·蒂皮特","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ジョー・ティペット","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"جو تیپت","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Τζο Τίπετ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"جو تيبيت","primary":false}}]}},"person_1402734_translations":{"at":1774370534932,"data":{"id":1402734,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yiu Wai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"姚炜本名金瑛瑛，四十年代末出生于上海。自幼爱好唱歌，一次在歌厅被歌唱老师许佩邀请上台代唱，从此一鸣惊人，获歌厅邀请加盟，并于1973年在港开始职业演唱。她曾是丽的电视的合约歌星，也曾与宝丽金签下唱片合约。姚炜常受邀到东南亚各地登台演出。与新加坡颇有渊源的姚炜，早年经常来新登台。曾受邀在台北大歌厅驻唱两年之久。 　　姚炜歌而优则演，于1978年签约香港无线电视。电视作品包括《势不两立》、《奋斗》、《无双谱》、《情谜》、《飞鹰》、《神探霹雳》、《北斗双雄》、《鳄鱼潭》等。此外，她也曾参演多部电影，如《金大班的最后一夜》、《塘西故事》、《再起风云》、《鬼域》、《鬼马智多星》、《鲨鱼烧卖》、《爱人女神》、《红番区》、《香江岁月》、《赤裸羔羊》及《海上花》等。她在《势不两立》中的豪门怨妇的角色，奠定了她在演艺圈的地位。 　　姚炜最受瞩目的代表作则是由白先勇名著改编而成的《金大班的最后一夜》。","name":"姚炜","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"姚煒本名金瑛瑛，四十年代末出生於上海。自幼愛好唱歌，一次在歌廳被歌唱老師許佩邀請上台代唱，從此一鳴驚人，獲歌廳邀請加盟，並於 1973 年在港開始職業演唱。她曾是麗的電視的合約歌星，也曾與寶麗金簽下唱片合約。姚煒常受邀到東南亞各地登台演出。與新加坡頗有淵源的姚煒，早年經常來新登台。曾受邀在台北大歌廳駐唱兩年之久。\n\n姚煒歌而優則演，於 1978 年簽約香港無線電視。電視作品包括《勢不兩立》、《奮鬥》、《無雙譜》、《情謎》、《飛鷹》、《神探霹靂》、《北鬥雙雄》、《鱷魚潭》等。此外，她也曾參演多部電影，如《金大班的最後一夜》、《塘西故事》、《再起風雲》、《鬼域》、《鬼馬智多星》、《鯊魚燒賣》、《愛人女神》、《紅番區》、《香江歲月》、《赤裸羔羊》及《海上花》等。她在《勢不兩立》中的豪門怨婦的角色，奠定了她在演藝圈的地位。\n\n姚煒最受矚目的代表作則是由白先勇名著改編而成的《金大班的最後一夜》。","name":"姚煒","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yiu Wai","primary":false}}]}},"person_4971510_translations":{"at":1774370549490,"data":{"id":4971510,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hwang Yong-wook","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hwang Yong-wook","primary":false}}]}},"person_4395204_translations":{"at":1774370561230,"data":{"id":4395204,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lauren Leppard","primary":true}}]}},"tv_298917_credits":{"at":1774370563743,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":3259638,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Pongsakorn Mettarikanon","original_name":"พงศกร เมตตาริกานนท์","popularity":0.998,"profile_path":"/u8NV6FOVRH2Z0XFswpYuX9ZDuXr.jpg","character":"Chalit","credit_id":"68a7f9785159c7c19a646391","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1259512,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Ranida Techasit","original_name":"Ranida Techasit","popularity":0.6474,"profile_path":"/qCNpr8XhHifA7eK8EICJFbnPl3c.jpg","character":"Pin Anong","credit_id":"68a7f980529408e58e8eda65","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":3727912,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Rapheephong Thapsuwan","original_name":"รพีพงศ์ ทับสุวรรณ","popularity":0.5782,"profile_path":"/1QxBINTe5wtYSDXmydPv0Tf6sXW.jpg","character":"Panthep","credit_id":"68a7f9ba78987a217c646357","order":2},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":3259639,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Nattasha Bunprachom","original_name":"